Abstract = {This paper presents a project-based learning strategy for teaching
   hardware/software co-design in modern Computer Engineering undergraduate
   courses. This kind of approach is considered by several recent
   pedagogical studies as the ideal strategy to support great learning
   achievements and to increase the proficiency of the students both in the
